CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 2, 1952, pg. 22, reads: "Trio Featured at Stadium - Sandra Deel, star of 'Annie Get Your Gun,' Civic Light Opera production, currently at the Stadium, runs through 'Moonshine Lullaby,' the number she does with Bradford Williams, Brue Jackson and Floyd Rollins. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Actors in Civic Light Opera production of "Annie Get Your Gun" Bradford Williams, Brue Jackson, and Floyd Rollins surrounding Sandra Deel, backstage
